http://perplexed.co.uk/993_contenteditable_cross_browser_wysiwyg.htm

Get Selected: var sText = document.selection.createRange();

Do format commands:
document.execCommand($command) or document.execCommand($command,null,$val)

command list:
Bold
Copy
Cut
Paste
CreateLink
CreateBookmark
Italic
BackColor
InsertHorizontalRule
InsertImage
JustifyCenter
Unlink
InsertUnorderedList
InsertParagraph

From - http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ms533049%28v=VS.85%29.aspx
http://www.quirksmode.org/dom/execCommand.html
